One fix is to call `__init__` properly:
```py
class MyException(Exception):
    def __init__(self,a, b):
        super(MyException, self).__init__(a, b)
```
Also make sure that this is in a module, otherwise you will need to do:
```py
class MyException(Exception):
    def __init__(self,a, b):
        super(type(self), self).__init__(a, b)
```

