If you look at admin [source code](https://github.com/django-import-export/django-import-export/blob/master/import_export/admin.py#L156-L159), your resource class can override `import_data`:

    def import_data(*args, **kwargs):
        self._user = kwargs.get('user', None)
        return super(import_data(*args, **kwargs))

and then use self._user in after_save_instance

